      • getSpectraByExperimentID

        public List<MascotGenericFile> getSpectraByExperimentID(long experimentID,
                                                        SpectrumFetchParameters.AnnotationType annotType,
                                                        boolean fromLibrary,
                                                        boolean saveToFile)
                                                 throws SQLException
        Method to extract spectra belonging to a specific experiment.
        Parameters:
        experimentID - the experiment ID.
        annotType - the annotation-related fetch setting, either one of AnnotationType.WITH_ANNOTATIONS, WITHOUT_ANNOTATIONS or IGNORE_ANNOTATIONS
        fromLibrary - true if the spectra shall be pulled from the spectral library, false when they shall be pulled from previous searches.
        saveToFile - if false the resulting spectra will contain no data apart from their ID
        Returns:
        List of MGF objects.
        Throws:
        SQLException - if a database error occurs
